subject: App won't start after update
body: After installing the latest update (v3.2.2), the application fails to start. It shows a loading screen for about 10 seconds then closes without any error message. I've tried reinstalling but the problem persists. Running Windows 10 Pro.

subject: Question about team pricing
body: We're a startup with 12 employees. Can you explain the difference between Team and Business plans? We need SSO and audit logs. What's the per-user cost for annual billing?

subject: MFA setup issues on new phone
body: I got a new phone and need to transfer my MFA settings. I have my backup codes but they don't seem to work. Can you help me reset MFA so I can set it up on my new device?

subject: Payment failed - card expired
body: My payment failed because my card expired. I've updated the card information but I'm still getting emails saying payment failed. Can you retry the charge? New card ending in 8765.

subject: File upload stuck at 99%
body: Every time I try to upload files larger than 10MB, the progress bar gets stuck at 99% and never completes. Smaller files work fine. I'm using the web interface on Safari 17.

subject: Change account owner
body: Our previous account owner (jane@oldcompany.com) has left the company. We need to transfer account ownership to mark@newowner.com. How do we proceed?

subject: Tax invoice needed
body: We need a proper tax invoice with our company VAT number for the last 6 months of payments. VAT number: EU123456789. Company: Nordic Solutions AB.

subject: Keyboard shortcuts not working
body: None of the keyboard shortcuts work in the editor. Ctrl+S doesn't save, Ctrl+Z doesn't undo, etc. I've checked the settings and shortcuts are enabled. Using Windows 11 with the desktop app.

subject: Account locked after failed attempts
body: My account got locked after I apparently entered the wrong password too many times. I'm certain I'm using the correct password now. How long until the lockout expires, or can you unlock it manually?

subject: Requesting enterprise trial extension
body: Our enterprise trial expires tomorrow but we haven't finished our evaluation. Can we get a 2-week extension? We're very interested but need to complete security review.

subject: Calendar sync issues with Outlook
body: Calendar events from your app aren't syncing to my Outlook calendar. I've authorized the connection and other integrations work fine. Using Outlook 365.

subject: Remove old team member
body: Please remove the user alex@former.employee from our team. They left the company last week and we want to ensure they can no longer access our workspace.

subject: Bulk discount inquiry
body: We're planning to purchase licenses for 200+ users. Do you offer volume discounts? Also interested in multi-year pricing options.

subject: SSL certificate error
body: Getting 'Your connection is not private' error when accessing the app. NET::ERR_CERT_DATE_INVALID. Is your SSL certificate expired or is this on my end?

subject: Merge duplicate accounts
body: I accidentally created two accounts with different emails. Can you merge john.doe@gmail.com and johndoe@work.com into one account? I want to keep the work email as primary.

subject: Report generation timeout
body: When generating monthly reports with more than 10,000 records, the system times out after 5 minutes. Can the timeout be increased or is there a way to generate these in batches?

subject: Annual billing switch
body: Currently on monthly billing at $15/user. Want to switch to annual billing. How do I do this and will I get credit for the current month's payment?

subject: Session expires too quickly
body: My session keeps expiring after only 15 minutes of inactivity, which is very disruptive. Can the session timeout be extended to at least 1 hour?

subject: Memory leak in desktop app
body: The desktop application's memory usage keeps growing over time. After a few hours, it's using 4GB+ RAM and becomes sluggish. I have to restart it multiple times a day.

subject: Payment method restrictions
body: We can only pay by wire transfer as our company policy doesn't allow credit card payments. Do you support wire transfers for annual subscriptions?
